115
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,080
would there be

116
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,240
something different between us?

117
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,240
Why do you ask?

118
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,560
