124
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,280
I saw Fu Yunyue.

125
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,560
Are you sure?

126
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,160
Fu Yunyue is still alive?

127
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,520
I saw her with my own eyes.

128
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:00,680
That wicked woman is really lucky.

129
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,600
Yunzheng,

130
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,760
why are you here?

131
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,840
I want you to meet someone.

132
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:17,840
Miss Shen, help me!

133
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,640
Miss Shen,

134
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,880
only you can save me.

135
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:20,840
Who are you?

136
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,040
I don't know you.

137
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,080
You paid me to abduct Moli

138
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,720
- and asked me to sell her.
- Shut up!

139
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,840
I don't know you at all.

140
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,440
Don't...

141
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,720
Yunzheng, I...

142
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,240
I just want you to know

143
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,560
if there's a next time,

144
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,360
you'll die worse than him.

145
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,160
Master, bad news.

146
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,240
Miss Zhiwei disappeared

147
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,120
on her way back.

148
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:22,320
What?

149
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:38,440
Zhiwei!

150
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,080
- Zhiwei!
- Miss Zhiwei!

151
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,160
Search inside.

152
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:41,920
Over there.

153
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,520
- Check over there.
- Shen Zhiwei!

154
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,320
Zhiwei!

155
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,520
Shen Zhiwei!

156
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,480
Look,

157
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,920
what's this?

158
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,400
This is my sister's hairpin.

159
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:06,880
It's Zhiwei's hairpin.

160
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,080
This way.

161
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,840
Follow me.

162
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,920
Stop, stop!

163
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,440
Zhiwei!

164
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,720
Zhiwei,

165
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,480
- Don't worry. Dad's here.
- Hurry!

166
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,680
Don't be afraid, sweetie.

167
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:25,040
Dad's here.

168
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:25,760
Don't be afraid.

169
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:28,320
Hurry up!

170
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,720
Careful, don't be afraid.

171
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,000
Tell me what happened.

172
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,160
