193
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,800
Zhiwei,

194
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:16,480
come home with me first.

195
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:17,840
But rest assured,

196
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,480
I

197
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:21,040
